    "body": "NAVAREA XIX 79/26\n\nNORWEGIAN SEA\n\nGRENNLAND SEA\n\n1. ROCKET LAUNCH OPERATION WILL BE CONDUCTED. 20:00- 21:00 UTC DAILY FROM 15 TO 21 JUN 26.\n\nMARITIME TRAFFIC IS REQUESTED TO BE AWARE OF THE FOLLOWING DANGER AREA.\n\nANDOEYA SPACE REQUESTS THAT NO VESSELS ARE PRESENT IN THE AREA FROM 17:00UTC TO 21:00 UTC\n\n\n\nIN AREAS BOUNDED BY:\n\n\n\nA. 68-59.33N 015-28.04E\n\nB. 69-13.36N 015-58.52E\n\nC. 70-53.82N 014-10.90E\n\nD. 70-41.62N 012-51.94E\n\nE. 68-59.33N 015-28.04E\n\n\n\nA. 71-03.42N 015-12.97E\n\nB. 74-15.83N 009-52.26E\n\nC. 76-50.36N 003-23.81E\n\nD. 79-11.76N 006-04.25W\n\nE. 79-55.85N 010-21.89W\n\nF. 79-41.45N 011-34.90W\n\nG. 78-03.47N 004-13.39W\n\nH. 76-01.02N 002-00.03E\n\nI. 73-32.12N 007-12.24E\n\nJ. 70-30.12N 011-37.50E\n\nK. 71-03.42N 015-12.97E\n\nL. 71-03.42N 015-12.97E\n\n\n\nFOR COORDINATION, CONTACT ANDOEYA SPACE CENTER.\n\nTELEPHONE +47 94 07 59 44 / +47 76 14 45 87 E-MAIL MSO@ANDOYASPACE.NO OR MARITIME VHF CH 14/16  WWW.ANDOYASPACE.NO\n\n2. REFERS NORWEGIAN NOTICES TO MARINERS 11/2026",
